   634→ * POST /scenarios/:id/promote
   635→ *
   636→ * Promote a scenario to become the new production baseline.
   637→ * This will:
   638→ * 1. Materialize all scenario deltas
   639→ * 2. Create a new published baseline
   640→ * 3. Apply the deltas to the production PM schedule
   641→ * 4. Mark the scenario as PROMOTED
